<dl><dd>Guno gwe muko ogusooka ogwa <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia" title="Wikipedia">Wikipedia</a> y'O<a href="/wiki/Luganda" title="Luganda">luganda</a>. Kaakano, Wikipedia eno erina abagikozesa batono, naye bw'oba ng'omanyi era ng'oyagala Oluganda, osobola okuyamba okuwandiika mu Wikipedia eno. Osobola okuwandiika empapula, oba okuvvuunula ezo eziri mu nnimi endala okuzizza mu Luganda, Osuubirwa okukyusa ebiwandiiko byonna ebiri mu Wikipedia y'Olungereza mu butuufu bwabyo.</dd></dl></div>

</p><p>Ate nabasubula kubano ababitusizza mu bibuga okubigya gyebirimirwa oba ku malundiro, nebabiguza ababirya consumers Abalimi bandifunye ssente nnyingi singa betundira ebirime nensolo zaabwe butereevu mu katale.     Bisangiddwa ku Wikipedia

    Tukusanyukidde ku Wikipediya
    Omukutu guno gwa bwereere era buli muntu asobola okuteekako obubaka n'ebirowoozo ku nsonga ez'enjawulo
    Kakaano mulimu ebiwandiiko 4,316 mu Luganda

    Guno gwe muko ogusooka ogwa Wikipedia y'Oluganda. Kaakano, Wikipedia eno erina abagikozesa batono, naye bw'oba ng'omanyi era ng'oyagala Oluganda, osobola okuyamba okuwandiika mu Wikipedia eno. Osobola okuwandiika empapula, oba okuvvuunula ezo eziri mu nnimi endala okuzizza mu Luganda, Osuubirwa okukyusa ebiwandiiko byonna ebiri mu Wikipedia y'Olungereza mu butuufu bwabyo.

    Ekiwandiiko ky'olunaku

    Omusubuzi owawakati abantu abawakati bebasubuzi abemirundi ebiri, abo abagula ebirime oba ebirundwa okuva ku balimi nabalunzi mubyalo, ate nabo nebabiguza abasubuzi abalejjalejja.

    Ate nabasubula kubano ababitusizza mu bibuga okubigya gyebirimirwa oba ku malundiro, nebabiguza ababirya consumers Abalimi bandifunye ssente nnyingi singa betundira ebirime nensolo zaabwe butereevu mu katale. Abalimi okutundira awamu nga beggasse kijja kuyamba nnyo abalimi nabalunzi era nabaguzi ababirya.

Bisangiddwa ku Wikipedia

Tukusanyukidde ku Wikipediya
Omukutu guno gwa bwereere era buli muntu asobola okuteekako obubaka n'ebirowoozo ku nsonga ez'enjawulo
Kakaano mulimu ebiwandiiko 4,316 mu Luganda

Guno gwe muko ogusooka ogwa Wikipedia y'Oluganda. Kaakano, Wikipedia eno erina abagikozesa batono, naye bw'oba ng'omanyi era ng'oyagala Oluganda, osobola okuyamba okuwandiika mu Wikipedia eno. Osobola okuwandiika empapula, oba okuvvuunula ezo eziri mu nnimi endala okuzizza mu Luganda, Osuubirwa okukyusa ebiwandiiko byonna ebiri mu Wikipedia y'Olungereza mu butuufu bwabyo.

Ekiwandiiko ky'olunaku

Omusubuzi owawakati abantu abawakati bebasubuzi abemirundi ebiri, abo abagula ebirime oba ebirundwa okuva ku balimi nabalunzi mubyalo, ate nabo nebabiguza abasubuzi abalejjalejja.

Ate nabasubula kubano ababitusizza mu bibuga okubigya gyebirimirwa oba ku malundiro, nebabiguza ababirya consumers Abalimi bandifunye ssente nnyingi singa betundira ebirime nensolo zaabwe butereevu mu katale. Abalimi okutundira awamu nga beggasse kijja kuyamba nnyo abalimi nabalunzi era nabaguzi ababirya.

Bisangiddwa ku Wikipedia
Tukusanyukidde ku [Wikipediya](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia "Wikipedia")  
Omukutu guno gwa bwereere era buli muntu asobola okuteekako obubaka n'ebirowoozo ku nsonga ez'enjawulo  
Kakaano mulimu ebiwandiiko **[4,316](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:Statistics "Special:Statistics")** mu [Luganda](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luganda "Luganda")     Guno gwe muko ogusooka ogwa [Wikipedia](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia "Wikipedia") y'O[luganda](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/Luganda "Luganda"). Kaakano, Wikipedia eno erina abagikozesa batono, naye bw'oba ng'omanyi era ng'oyagala Oluganda, osobola okuyamba okuwandiika mu Wikipedia eno. Osobola okuwandiika empapula, oba okuvvuunula ezo eziri mu nnimi endala okuzizza mu Luganda, Osuubirwa okukyusa ebiwandiiko byonna ebiri mu Wikipedia y'Olungereza mu butuufu bwabyo.

## Ekiwandiiko ky'olunaku  
---  
[![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/59/Fish_Ponds_and_Rice_Fields%2C_Lower_Guadalquivir_River.jpg/250px-Fish_Ponds_and_Rice_Fields%2C_Lower_Guadalquivir_River.jpg)](https://lg.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Fish_Ponds_and_Rice_Fields,_Lower_Guadalquivir_River.jpg) **Omusubuzi owawakati** abantu abawakati bebasubuzi abemirundi ebiri, abo abagula ebirime oba ebirundwa okuva ku balimi nabalunzi mubyalo, ate nabo nebabiguza abasubuzi abalejjalejja.  Ate nabasubula kubano ababitusizza mu bibuga okubigya gyebirimirwa oba ku malundiro, nebabiguza ababirya consumers Abalimi bandifunye ssente nnyingi singa betundira ebirime nensolo zaabwe butereevu mu katale. Abalimi okutundira awamu nga beggasse kijja kuyamba nnyo abalimi nabalunzi era nabaguzi ababirya.

Bisangiddwa ku Wikipedia
Tukusanyukidde ku Wikipediya39  
Omukutu guno gwa bwereere era buli muntu asobola okuteekako obubaka n'ebirowoozo ku nsonga ez'enjawulo  
Kakaano mulimu ebiwandiiko **4,31640** mu Luganda41     Guno gwe muko ogusooka ogwa Wikipedia39 y'Oluganda41. Kaakano, Wikipedia eno erina abagikozesa batono, naye bw'oba ng'omanyi era ng'oyagala Oluganda, osobola okuyamba okuwandiika mu Wikipedia eno. Osobola okuwandiika empapula, oba okuvvuunula ezo eziri mu nnimi endala okuzizza mu Luganda, Osuubirwa okukyusa ebiwandiiko byonna ebiri mu Wikipedia y'Olungereza mu butuufu bwabyo.

---

Ate nabasubula kubano ababitusizza mu bibuga okubigya gyebirimirwa oba ku malundiro, nebabiguza ababirya consumers Abalimi bandifunye ssente nnyingi singa betundira ebirime nensolo zaabwe butereevu mu katale. Abalimi okutundira awamu nga beggasse kijja kuyamba nnyo abalimi nabalunzi era nabaguzi ababirya.
